These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, crime
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, airplane
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | crime |
| Transport     | airplane | scooter  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, blueberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, rowing
1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | cauliflower      | blueberry         |
| Sport   | surfing | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up
There 2 different types of food: avocado, apple
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee   |
| Food       | apple  | avocado |

 #################################

 
